{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": [{"tool_use_id": "chatcmpl-tool-9d7a4340091ceb83", "type": "tool_result", "content": "# SemanticVocoder: Bridging Audio Generation and Audio Understanding via Semantic Latents\narXiv: 2602.23333\nAuthors: Zeyu Xie, Chenxing Li, Qiao Jin, Xuenan Xu, Guanrou Yang, Wenfu Wang, Mengyue Wu, Dong Yu, Yuexian Zou\nYear: 2026 | Venue: \nTopic: vocoder\nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. SemanticVocoder directly generates waveforms from semantic latents, eliminating reliance on VAE modules and their associated negative impacts.\n  2. The text-to-audio system powered by SemanticVocoder achieves state-of-the-art performance on AudioCaps with a Fréchet Distance of 12.823 and a Fréchet Audio Distance of 1.709.\n  3. SemanticVocoder bridges audio generation and understanding by enabling both tasks to be modeled within a shared semantic latent space.\n\nTags: Vocoder, Vocoder/Diffusion", "is_error": false}]}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "ad91271d-9395-4deb-ae68-573cc188887a", "uuid": "95a35f33-f49b-43ea-a9b6-b2f81802a03b", "timestamp": "2026-07-16T08:19:00.142Z", "tool_use_result": {"stdout": "# SemanticVocoder: Bridging Audio Generation and Audio Understanding via Semantic Latents\narXiv: 2602.23333\nAuthors: Zeyu Xie, Chenxing Li, Qiao Jin, Xuenan Xu, Guanrou Yang, Wenfu Wang, Mengyue Wu, Dong Yu, Yuexian Zou\nYear: 2026 | Venue: \nTopic: vocoder\nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. SemanticVocoder directly generates waveforms from semantic latents, eliminating reliance on VAE modules and their associated negative impacts.\n  2. The text-to-audio system powered by SemanticVocoder achieves state-of-the-art performance on AudioCaps with a Fréchet Distance of 12.823 and a Fréchet Audio Distance of 1.709.\n  3. SemanticVocoder bridges audio generation and understanding by enabling both tasks to be modeled within a shared semantic latent space.\n\nTags: Vocoder, Vocoder/Diffusion", "stderr": "", "interrupted": false, "isImage": false, "noOutputExpected": false}}
{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": [{"tool_use_id": "chatcmpl-tool-8e26cfb8b0896372", "type": "tool_result", "content": "# \narXiv: 2605.00329\nAuthors: \nYear: 0 | Venue: \nTopic: tts_vc\nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. The energy-distance objective is applied to text-to-audio generation for the first time, enabling low-latency one-step latent synthesis.\n  2. An auxiliary distillation loss aligns feature representations from a diffusion-based teacher transformer with the energy-based student model, yielding consistent improvements across all objective metrics.\n  3. The proposed model outperforms existing few-step sampling baselines on both objective and subjective metrics while narrowing the quality gap to multi-step diffusion systems.\n\nTags: TTS, TTS/架构-NAR-Diffusion, TTS/功能-蒸馏加速, TTS/功能-快速生成", "is_error": false}]}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "ad91271d-9395-4deb-ae68-573cc188887a", "uuid": "dfe3af1e-427d-411e-9729-4a226580a974", "timestamp": "2026-07-16T08:19:00.392Z", "tool_use_result": {"stdout": "# \narXiv: 2605.00329\nAuthors: \nYear: 0 | Venue: \nTopic: tts_vc\nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. The energy-distance objective is applied to text-to-audio generation for the first time, enabling low-latency one-step latent synthesis.\n  2. An auxiliary distillation loss aligns feature representations from a diffusion-based teacher transformer with the energy-based student model, yielding consistent improvements across all objective metrics.\n  3. The proposed model outperforms existing few-step sampling baselines on both objective and subjective metrics while narrowing the quality gap to multi-step diffusion systems.\n\nTags: TTS, TTS/架构-NAR-Diffusion, TTS/功能-蒸馏加速, TTS/功能-快速生成", "stderr": "", "interrupted": false, "isImage": false, "noOutputExpected": false}}
